        <release version="4.9.2" date="2025-06-26">
            <description>
                <p>On the way to 5.0, the existing code has undergone some significant restructuring and profiling. Instead of keeping all of these performance improvements and bug fixes for v5.0, another minor release, v4.9.2, provides access to these changes much earlier.</p>
            </description>
