        </release>
        <release version="4.9.1" date="2025-05-06">
            <description>
                <p>PhotoQt 4.9 had a lot of exciting changes and additions. Unfortunately there were also some bugs that slipped through. This release, v4.9.1, fixes a whole range of them making PhotoQt better than ever before.</p>
            </description>
            <url>
                https://photoqt.org/news/photoqt-4.9.1
            </url>
        </release>
        <release version="4.9" date="2025-04-23">
            <description>
                <p>A new release for PhotoQt is ready with a bunch of additions and improvements and several bug fixes. This is a very exciting release, as there are some very exciting changes packed in it. Looking ahead, some big changes are in the works for v5.0.</p>
            </description>
            <url>
                https://photoqt.org/news/photoqt-4.9
            </url>
        </release>
        <release version="4.8.1" date="2025-02-13">
            <description>
